name: Edward Knueppel Jr.
text: Gotta love a giant take n bake pizza that is way cheaper than delivery.

name: Dean Hoover
text: They do a very good job here.  Service is always good, and they make a fine pizza!

name: Desiree La Belle
text: I enjoyed the stuffed pizza....  I thought it was stuffed crust but.... It was literally like a huge pocket pizza lol. It was good and tasted fresh!!! Good deals as well.

name: Pam Wollert
text: Employees are outstanding...saw one employee helping a customer who walked with a cane and needed help take their pizza to the car and put it inside the give them a hand getting off the curb safely and in their car. What awesome customer service!!! Great job!!!

name: Dave Morris
text:
Made our own. Pan, Garlic white sauce, ground sausage, bacon, dried tomatoes, spinach & extra mozz.
They should make it one of their signatures, it was nom, nom, nom

name: Todd Schleh
text:
I have a GREAT STAFF at this Waukesha Papa Murphy's, and all of us starting with my GM Marissa are ready to make your favorite pizza!
What is your favorite pizza? Let us make it for you today!

name: Regena Wolter
text: I would not recommend this place since they got a new manager. They treat their employee's with special needs terrible. Not going to endorse a place with mediocre pizza and bad practice.

text:
